{"tid":1305694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班人少少事就打曬飛機咁","createTime":"2019-07-11T02:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:56.000Z","uid":91866,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ac627c4c4536982b480b544aa7dd04282d0b01","tid":1305694,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"寶礦力撒出個廣告姐有咩咁大件事？人地都要賺錢 見到你地成班人咁樣話抵制tvb換著你係廣告商都驚到仆街啦？咁有咩好值得吹奏打飛機？不如對返岩個焦點係遊行升級到先啦？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人有樣野唔好就係太善忘</span><br />\n<br />\n來緊星期遊行又未宣傳夠就打曬飛機咁以為大獲全勝 又一堆撚樣係呢d敏感時期玩膠 對唔對得住一班犧牲左既烈士？矛頭係咪應該對返準政府？來緊已經話要社會信用評分系統 到依架d人寧願出去守連儂牆都唔寧願去做文宣  連儂牆只係拎來打下氣無咩實際用途 <br />\n     最後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下香港人快d醒下準備來緊既夢境啦</span>"},{"pid":"8ab1baa04626fad921e5dc6be3da7a2129c1a534","tid":1305694,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd44a3a6b8c5f5beab1d8f9956d45eef6d24c98","tid":1305694,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3147a08c78d92672e254137de27917fb5c9cb45f","tid":1305694,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f3f0a43469281a2a7e78999b3414235686bc44","tid":1305694,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48a98d970c9